org.cornutum.tcases.generator

Class TupleGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cornutum.tcases.generator.TupleGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITestCaseGenerator, CloneableType<ITestCaseGenerator>

    public class TupleGenerator
extends Object
implements ITestCaseGenerator
    Generates test cases for a function that use all specified N-tuples of valid variable values.
